title: 60's Beat Girls Collection Vol 1 Japanese Pop Cuties In S
description:
Review from Amazon.com:
"Dig It!"
If you're a fan of go go boots, miniskirts, and 60's pop I highly recommend this cd. I don't know who is on it as it is written in Japanese. And I have no idea what they're saying. All I know is that I dig the way they say it baby!
